import { createStore } from 'redux' const notificationReducer = (state = "testing", action) => { switch(action.type) { case 'USER_ERROR': return
'You entered the wrong username or password'
case 'RESET': return state case 'BLOG_ADDED': return 'You added a new blog' default: return state } } const notificationStore = createStore(notificationReducer) export default notificationStore
